Hi TeeJay,

They don't necessarily represent abbreviations of words, which is
probably why you're having trouble finding words.  An 'X' is just an
X, and a 'V' appears to be half an X.  

We've collected a bunch of links with information about Roman Numerals
here:

  http://mathforum.org/dr.math/faq/faq.roman.html

Does this help? 

- Doctor Ian, The Math Forum
  <http://mathforum.org/dr.math/>

